{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d1de775d2b","title":"致彭德怀电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f7948f23b6","index":0,"year":1936,"month":10,"day":26,"articleId":"d1de775d2b"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2a30265034","type":"paragraph","text":"致彭德怀电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d1de775d2b"},{"id":"9a012fd018","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年10月26日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d1de775d2b"},{"id":"1cd934822c","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）国泰有出凉州不愿出宁夏之意，望注意。（二）目前以打击胡敌、夺取定远营两着为最重要。（三）三十军占领永登是对的。九军必须占定远营，这是接物攻宁的战略板纽，不应以一方面军去占，不便利，又失时机。（四）四、五、三十一军，二方面军，应以打胡为中心，仅抗击不够，打法可采诱敌深入。（五）一方面军速集结同心城休息。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d1de775d2b"},{"id":"6e8c5efed4","type":"paragraph","text":"1这是毛泽东致彭德怀电的主要内容。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d1de775d2b"}],"page":{"id":"5fd9194555","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d1de775d2b","start":258,"end":258}}}},"__N_SSG":true}